{
	"nodes": [
		{
			"id": "title",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "# VAULT PROCESS FLOW — Scripts × Lib Modules × Agents × Data Pulls",
			"x": 0,
			"y": 0,
			"width": 5760,
			"height": 70,
			"color": "4"
		},
		{
			"id": "lbl_src",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "# EXTERNAL DATA SOURCES",
			"x": 0,
			"y": 80,
			"width": 5760,
			"height": 70,
			"color": "3"
		},
		{
			"id": "src_market",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## Financial Modeling Prep (FMP)\n\n- Daily OHLCV bars (260–420 days)\n- Intraday 1-min bars\n- Company profile, float, short interest\n- Income statement, cash flow, balance sheet\n- Stock news headlines\n- Insider trades, institutional ownership\n- TTM ratios, analyst estimates\n\n**Key:** `FINANCIAL_MODELING_PREP_API_KEY`",
			"x": 0,
			"y": 150,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "3"
		},
		{
			"id": "src_macro",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## FRED + CBOE\n\n**FRED** (St. Louis Fed)\n- Federal funds rate\n- 10Y–2Y yield curve spread\n- VIX (CBOE Volatility Index)\n- HY credit spreads\n\n**CBOE** (CSV endpoint)\n- Daily put/call ratio\n- Skew index\n- VIX term structure\n\n**Key:** `FRED_API_KEY`",
			"x": 960,
			"y": 150,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "3"
		},
		{
			"id": "src_sec",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## SEC EDGAR\n\n*(No API key required)*\n\n- Company facts (XBRL)\n- Annual / quarterly filings\n  (10-K, 10-Q, 8-K)\n- S-3 shelf registrations\n- Form 4 insider filings\n- Full-text EFTS search\n- Ticker ↔ CIK mapping\n\nAccessed via `edgar.mjs` +\n`cik-map.mjs`",
			"x": 1920,
			"y": 150,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "3"
		},
		{
			"id": "src_bio",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## Biotech & Research APIs\n\n**openFDA**\n- Drug approvals, adverse events\n- Recalls and enforcement\n\n**ClinicalTrials.gov** *(no key)*\n- Trial registrations\n- Phase, status, enrollment\n\n**NCBI PubMed** *(no key)*\n- Scientific literature search\n\n**Key:** `FDA_OPEN_DATA_API_KEY`",
			"x": 2880,
			"y": 150,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "3"
		},
		{
			"id": "src_news",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## News & Research APIs\n\n**NewsAPI**\n- Breaking headline search\n- Keyword + source filtering\n\n**arXiv** *(no key)*\n- Preprint paper search\n- Atom feed query\n\n**OpenAlex** *(no key)*\n- Academic research graph\n\n**OSINT feeds**\n- Reddit (pushshift / native)\n- Telegram channels\n- OpenCorporates\n\n**Key:** `NEWSAPI_API_KEY`",
			"x": 3840,
			"y": 150,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "3"
		},
		{
			"id": "src_gov",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## Government & Energy APIs\n\n**EIA** (Energy Information Admin)\n- Electricity generation / demand\n- Natural gas, petroleum\n\n**BEA** (Bureau of Economic Analysis)\n- GDP, personal income\n\n**SAM.gov** — federal contracts\n\n**FPDS** — procurement data\n\n**OpenFEMA** *(no key)*\n- Disaster declarations\n\n**Keys:** `EIA_API_KEY`, `BEA_API_KEY`,\n`SAM_GOV_API_KEY`",
			"x": 4800,
			"y": 150,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "3"
		},
		{
			"id": "lbl_lib",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "# LIB MODULES  (`scripts/lib/`)",
			"x": 0,
			"y": 940,
			"width": 5760,
			"height": 70,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "lib_fmp",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## fmp-client.mjs\n\nFMP REST wrapper\n\n**Exports**\n- `getHistoricalPrices(sym, days)`\n- `getIntradayBars(sym, interval)`\n- `getProfile(sym)` — float, mktcap\n- `getFinancials(sym)` — IS/CF/BS\n- `getStockNews(sym, limit)`\n- `getShortInterest(sym)`\n- `getInsiderTrades(sym)`\n- `getTTMRatios(sym)`\n\nUsed by: price, risk, fund, sent,\nmicro agents + most pullers",
			"x": 0,
			"y": 1010,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "lib_edgar",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## edgar.mjs + cik-map.mjs\n\n`edgar.mjs`\n- `getCompanyFacts(cik)`\n- `getFilings(cik, forms)`\n- `getShelfCapacity(cik)` — S-3 math\n- Full-text EFTS search wrapper\n\n`cik-map.mjs`\n- Ticker → CIK lookup\n- Cached bulk company tickers JSON\n\n`dilution-rules.mjs`\n- Shelf capacity math\n- Overhang % calculation\n- Alert threshold logic",
			"x": 960,
			"y": 1010,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "lib_fetch",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## fetcher.mjs + bars.mjs\n\n`fetcher.mjs`\n- `fetchJSON(url, opts)` — retry + timeout\n- `fetchAll(tasks)` — concurrent map\n- Rate-limit aware (configurable)\n\n`bars.mjs`\n- OHLCV normalization\n- ATR14 calculation\n- Relative volume computation\n\n`markdown.mjs`\n- Note builder (headers, tables)\n- Frontmatter injection\n\n`obsidian-cli.mjs`\n- Set frontmatter properties via\n  Obsidian Local REST API",
			"x": 1920,
			"y": 1010,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "lib_llm",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## llm-client.mjs\n\nClaude API integration\n\n**Exports**\n- `chatJSON(system, user)` —\n  returns parsed JSON from Claude\n- JSON-mode enforcement via\n  system prompt contract\n- Model: claude-sonnet-4-6\n\nUsed exclusively by\n`synthesis-agent.mjs` to produce\nthe final BULLISH / BEARISH /\nNEUTRAL verdict + status tier",
			"x": 2880,
			"y": 1010,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "lib_config",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## config.mjs + system libs\n\n`config.mjs`\n- `.env` loader (dotenv)\n- `getVaultRoot()` — vault path\n- `getPullsDir()` — `05_Data_Pulls/`\n- `getSignalsDir()` — `06_Signals/`\n- `getApiKey(sourceId)` — key registry\n\n`sector-map.mjs`\n- Ticker → sector/industry\n\n`schema.mjs`\n- Zod schemas for pull frontmatter\n\n`kb-bridge.mjs`\n- Knowledge base integration shim",
			"x": 3840,
			"y": 1010,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "lib_mm",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## MarketMind signal libs\n\n`entropy.mjs`\n- Shannon entropy over OHLCV bins\n- Normalized 0–1 score\n- `sessionEntropy(bars)` export\n\n`scoring.mjs`\n- Deterministic weighted sum of\n  7 agent confidence scores\n- Weights from `config/scoring-weights.json`\n\n`schemas.mjs`\n- Signal object shape:\n  `{ confidence, direction, summary, raw_data }`\n\n`utils.mjs`\n- Formatting helpers, verdict labels",
			"x": 4800,
			"y": 1010,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "6"
		},
		{
			"id": "lbl_pull",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "# PULLER SCRIPTS  (`scripts/pullers/`)",
			"x": 0,
			"y": 1800,
			"width": 5760,
			"height": 70,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "pull_market",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## Market Pullers\n\n`orb-entropy.mjs`\nORB trade sheet — 9:35 AM daily\nBuilds 5-min open-range candle,\napplies entropy + gap + VWAP filters\n\n`rel-vol-screen.mjs`\nTop 20 by relative volume (9:00 AM)\n\n`entropy-compression-scan.mjs`\n~774-symbol nightly scan;\nflags sustained compression ≤ 0.50\n\n`backtest-orb-eod.mjs`\nEnd-of-day ORB strategy backtest\n\n`earnings-entropy.mjs`\nIntraday entropy before earnings\n\n`outcome-review.mjs`\nReviews recent signal outcomes",
			"x": 0,
			"y": 1870,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "pull_fund",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## Fundamentals Pullers\n\n`dilution-monitor.mjs`\nBatch shelf capacity scan;\ntracks ATM overhang + dilution risk;\nwrites `06_Signals/` notes directly\n\n`dd-report.mjs`\nOne-click due diligence —\nIPO, ownership, float, filings\n\n`capital-raise.mjs`\nDaily offerings sweep (S-3, S-1)\n\n`disclosure-reality.mjs`\nRanks EDGAR filings by materiality\n\n`company-risk-scan.mjs`\nFundamental + regulatory +\nsentiment risk events",
			"x": 960,
			"y": 1870,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "pull_macro",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## Macro Pullers\n\n`fred.mjs`\nFRED series snapshot:\nFed funds, 10Y-2Y, VIX proxy,\nHY spreads, unemployment\n\n`eia.mjs`\nEnergy: weekly petroleum,\nelectricity demand, NG storage\n\n`bea.mjs`\nGDP, personal income,\nPCE deflator\n\n`cboe.mjs`\nDaily put/call ratio, skew,\nVIX term structure snapshot",
			"x": 1920,
			"y": 1870,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "pull_bio",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## Biotech & Research Pullers\n\n`fda.mjs`\nDrug approvals (PDUFA dates),\nadverse events, recalls\n\n`arxiv.mjs`\nPreprint search by keyword;\nreturns abstracts + metadata\n\n`clinicaltrials.mjs`\nTrial registrations by drug /\nsponsor; phase + status\n\n`pubmed.mjs`\nNCBI literature search;\nreturns citations + abstracts",
			"x": 2880,
			"y": 1870,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "pull_osint",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## OSINT & Media Pullers\n\n`newsapi.mjs`\nKeyword headline sweep;\nsentiment tagging\n\n`reddit.mjs`\nSubreddit scanner (pushshift /\nnative API); tracks mentions\n\n`telegram.mjs`\nChannel monitor via\nTelegram MTProto\n\n`opensecrets.mjs`\nPolitical contribution\nand lobbying data\n\n`signal-tracker.mjs`\nReads `06_Signals/` and\nsurfaces active alerts",
			"x": 3840,
			"y": 1870,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "pull_gov",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## Government & Energy Pullers\n\n`sam.mjs`\nSAM.gov contract awards\nand debarment records\n\n`fpds.mjs`\nFederal procurement data;\ncontractor spend by agency\n\n`fema.mjs`\nOpenFEMA disaster declarations\n+ individual assistance data\n\n`convergence-scan.mjs`\nReads alert/critical notes\nacross all domains; fires\n`06_Signals/` convergence note\nwhen 3+ domains flag same thesis",
			"x": 4800,
			"y": 1870,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "lbl_mm",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "# MARKETMIND AGENT PIPELINE  (`scripts/agents/marketmind/`)",
			"x": 0,
			"y": 2660,
			"width": 5760,
			"height": 70,
			"color": "4"
		},
		{
			"id": "mm_agents",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## Specialist Agents — parallel execution\nEach produces `{ confidence: 0–1, direction, summary, raw_data }`\n\n| Agent | Script | Data Source | Signal Focus |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| Price | `price-agent.mjs` | FMP 260–420 bars | SMA, EMA, MACD, RSI, Bollinger |\n| Risk | `risk-agent.mjs` | FMP price + profile | Volatility, max drawdown, Sharpe |\n| Fundamentals | `fundamentals-agent.mjs` | FMP IS/CF/BS | Margins, growth, debt load |\n| Sentiment | `sentiment-agent.mjs` | FMP news + NewsAPI | Keyword bullish/bearish scoring |\n| Macro | `macro-agent.mjs` | FRED | Yield curve, VIX, HY spreads |\n| Microstructure | `microstructure-agent.mjs` | FMP 1-min bars | Entropy, float, positioning |\n| Prediction Market | `prediction-market-agent.mjs` | Event APIs | Corporate event consensus |",
			"x": 0,
			"y": 2730,
			"width": 3780,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "4"
		},
		{
			"id": "mm_synth",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## synthesis-agent.mjs\n\n**Claude LLM** (JSON-mode)\n\nReads all 7 confidence scores\n+ deterministic weighted sum\nfrom `scoring.mjs`\n\n↓\n\n**BULLISH / BEARISH / NEUTRAL**\n\nstatus tier:\n`clear` · `watch` · `alert` · `critical`\n\nReturns structured JSON verdict",
			"x": 3840,
			"y": 2730,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "1"
		},
		{
			"id": "mm_orch",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## agent-analyst.mjs\n\nOrchestrator\n\nRuns all 8 agents in parallel\nfor a given symbol/thesis\n\nWrites pull note:\n`05_Data_Pulls/\n YYYY-MM-DD_\n Agent_Analysis_{sym}.md`\n\nAlso feeds:\n`convergence-scan.mjs`\nwhich reads alert/critical\nnotes for multi-domain signals",
			"x": 4800,
			"y": 2730,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "1"
		},
		{
			"id": "lbl_out",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "# DATA PULL OUTPUTS  (`05_Data_Pulls/`  ·  `06_Signals/`)",
			"x": 0,
			"y": 3520,
			"width": 5760,
			"height": 70,
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "out_market",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## 05_Data_Pulls/Market/\n\nTimestamped markdown notes:\n\n- `YYYY-MM-DD_ORB_Entropy_Screen.md`\n- `YYYY-MM-DD_FMP_RelVol_Screen.md`\n- `YYYY-MM-DD_Entropy_Compression_Scan.md`\n- `YYYY-MM-DD_Entropy_Backtest_*.md`\n- `YYYY-MM-DD_Agent_Analysis_{sym}.md`\n\nFrontmatter includes:\n`domain`, `signal_status`, `signals[]`,\n`agent_owner`, `date_pulled`",
			"x": 0,
			"y": 3590,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "out_fund",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## 05_Data_Pulls/Fundamentals/\n\nTimestamped markdown notes:\n\n- `YYYY-MM-DD_Dilution_Monitor.md`\n- `YYYY-MM-DD_DD_Report_{sym}.md`\n- `YYYY-MM-DD_Capital_Raise.md`\n- `YYYY-MM-DD_Disclosure_Reality.md`\n\nAlso writes per-ticker signal notes\ndirectly to `06_Signals/` when\ndilution thresholds are breached",
			"x": 960,
			"y": 3590,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "out_macro",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## 05_Data_Pulls/Macro/\n\nTimestamped markdown notes:\n\n- `YYYY-MM-DD_FRED_Snapshot.md`\n- `YYYY-MM-DD_EIA_Weekly.md`\n- `YYYY-MM-DD_BEA_GDP.md`\n- `YYYY-MM-DD_CBOE_Options.md`\n\n**Also feeds:**\n05_Data_Pulls/Energy/\n05_Data_Pulls/Government/",
			"x": 1920,
			"y": 3590,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "out_backtest",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## 05_Data_Pulls/Backtest/\n\nTimestamped markdown notes:\n\n- `YYYY-MM-DD_ORB_EOD_Backtest.md`\n\n- Strategy performance tables\n- Parameter sweep results\n- Equity curve data",
			"x": 2880,
			"y": 3590,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "out_bio",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## 05_Data_Pulls/Biotech/ + Research/\n\n`Biotech/`\n- FDA approval / PDUFA watches\n- Clinical trial updates\n- Adverse event flags\n\n`Research/`\n- arXiv preprint sweeps\n- PubMed literature alerts\n\n**Also:**\n05_Data_Pulls/News/\n05_Data_Pulls/OSINT/",
			"x": 3840,
			"y": 3590,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "out_signals",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "## 06_Signals/\n\nDiscrete signal notes — written when\nconfidence exceeds threshold:\n\n`YYYY-MM-DD_DILUTION_{SYM}.md`\n`YYYY-MM-DD_Convergence.md`\n`YYYY-MM-DD_AGENT_{SYM}.md`\n\n**Status tiers:**\n`critical` — immediate attention\n`alert` — monitor closely\n`watch` — track progression\n`clear` — resolved / no action\n\nRead by: Orchestrator Agent,\nSignal Board, convergence-scan",
			"x": 4800,
			"y": 3590,
			"width": 900,
			"height": 700,
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "lbl_agt",
			"type": "text",
